+ Stukje in profiel schrijven over individueel project
- Android app in gitlab zetten

DATABASE
- Docker file opstellen voor MySQL server
- Script opstellen dat MySQL database opzet voor waypoints

DIRECTIONS VIEW:
- Clickable tab on bottom
 - Expanding fragment when clicking

WEATHER UPDATE
- Weather Fragment: opmaak
- Weather Fragment: API call naar mediator bouwen
 - Mediator: API call naar openweathermap
 - Mediator: Logic upon response
 - Mediator: Response to app
- Weather Fragment: output logic

SHOWING ROUTES
- Explore Fragment: call to mediator for map
 - Mediator: Call naar database voor routes met start of eindpunten in requested zoom range
 - Mediator: API call naar mapquest voor kaart
  - met scrollable kaart
  - pin voor huidige locatie
  - stippen voor waypoints van route
  - lines voor routes op de kaart
 - Explore Fragment: output scrollable map
 - Explore Fragment: output pin for location
 - Explore Fragment: output lines for routes on map
 
SELECTING A ROUTE
- Explore Fragment: when clicking on line for route, zoom in on route
 - Explore Fragment: call to mediator for new map
  - Mediator: API call naar mapquest voor kaart
   - met scrollable kaart
   - pin voor huidige locatie (als in zoomview)
   - pin A voor begin van route
   - pin B voor eind van route
   - stippen voor waypoints van route
   - lines voor route
 - Explore Fragment: when selecting route, show Options Window

OPTIONS WINDOW TO GET DIRECTIONS
[A-B]
- Options window: button for requesting directions of route
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
[B-A]
- Options window: button for requesting directions of route
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
[here-A]
- Options window: button for requesting directions to A
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
[here-B]
- Options window: button for requesting directions to B
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
[here-A-B]
- Options window: button for requesting directions through A to B through the route
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
[here-B-A]
- Options window: button for requesting directions through B to A through the route
 - Call naar mediator
 - Mediator Call to database for all waypoints
 - Mediator Call to navigation API for route through waypoints
 - Response from mediator
 - Directions in Current Directions view
 
 
